original: Elling, Kaj Bertil, tandläkare. Bengtsfors, f. 12/2/18 i Gbg av avd:-chef Sven o. Meianie Elling. G. 45 m. Liil-Astri Stuge. Barn: Marie-Louise f. 46. — Studiex. v. Gbgs h. real 38, tandl :ex. 45, Aman. v. tandl :inst. tandfylln :avd. 45, anst. v. folktandv. i Mölndal 45-46, egen tandl :prakt. i Bengtsfors m. biprakt. i Dals-Långed sed. 46. Led. av Sv:es tandl :förb. lokalavd. Västgöta-Dal 46, led. av Sim avd. 1902 i Gbg sed. 28, led. av Dailsilands motorkl. 46, led. av AU. Frangaise i Gbg 38-39, dessutom led. av div. ddrifören. Hobby: -sport. Div. med. o. utmärkit i idro-tt.
translated: Elling, Kaj Bertil, dentist. Bengtsfors, born on February 12th, 1918 in Gothenburg to department head Sven and Meianie Elling. Married in 1945 to Liil-Astri Stuge, they have one child, Marie-Louise born in 1946. He graduated from Gothenburg's secondary school in 1938, received his dental degree in 1945, and apprenticed at the dental department in 1945. He worked for the public dental service in Mölndal from 1945-1946 before starting his own dental practice in Bengtsfors with a secondary practice in Dals-Långed since 1946. He is a member of Sweden's dental association and the local division of Västgöta-Dal since 1946, a member of the sim department since 1928, a member of the Dalslands motor club since 1946, a member of AU. Frangaise in Gothenburg from 1938-1939, as well as a member of various other sports clubs and organizations. His hobbies include sports. He has received various medical and athletic awards.
